en.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aFamily violencezUnited States. 0aSouth Asian American womenxServices forzUnited States. 0aSouth Asian American womenxViolence againstzUnited States. 0aSouth Asian AmericansxSocial conditions. 0aVictims of family violencezUnited States. 0aWomen immigrantsxLegal status, laws, etczUnited States. 0aWomen immigrantsxViolence againstzUnited States. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aAyyub, Ruksana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAyyub, Ruksana.1 aBhuyan, Rupaleem, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBhuyan, Rupaleem.1 aChoudhury, Prajna Paramita, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChoudhury, Prajna.1 aChowdhury, Elora Halim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChowdhury, Elora Halim.1 aDasgupta, Shamita Das, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDasgupta, Shamita Das, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aDasgupta, Shamita Das.1 aGrewal, Mandeep, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrewal, Mandeep.1 aHunjan, Sandeep, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHunjan, Sandeep.1 aJain, Shashi, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJain, Shashi.1 aJesudason, Sujatha Anbuselvi, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJesudason, Sujatha Anbuselvi.1 aKallivayalil, Diya, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKallivayalil, Diya.1 aPoore, Grace, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPoore, Grace.1 aPuri, Sunita, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPuri, Sunita